title: He’s not going to ask again... #MobLand

author: Paramount Plus
description:
Power is up for grabs as two warring crime families clash in a battle that threatens to topple empires and ruin lives. In the crossfire stands Harry Da Souza (Tom Hardy), a street-smart ‘fixer’ who knows too well where loyalties lie when opposing forces collide.

MOBLAND also stars Pierce Brosnan as Conrad Harrigan, the head of an organized crime family, and Helen Mirren as Maeve Harrigan, the brains behind her husband Conrad’s operation. As kingdom goes up against kingdom, lines will be crossed - and the only saving grace is a bet-your-life guarantee: family above everything.

MobLand is now streaming on Paramount+.
